<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="79" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="79">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="79">
The species was originally described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Liang, ZQ" journalOrPublisher="Mycosystema" pageId="0" pageNumber="79" pagination="306 - 309" refId="B50" refString="Liang, ZQ, Liu, AY, Jiang, YC, 2001. Two new species of Cordyceps from Jinggang Mountains. Mycosystema 20 (3): 306 - 309" title="Two new species of Cordyceps from Jinggang Mountains." volume="20" year="2001">Liang et al. (2001)</bibRefCitation>
with specimens from Jiangxi, China. 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.3114/sim.2007.57.01" author="Sung, GH" journalOrPublisher="Studies in Mycology" pageId="0" pageNumber="79" pagination="5 - 69" refId="B89" refString="Sung, GH, Hywel-Jones, NL, Sung, JM, Luangsa-ard, JJ, Shrestha, B, Spatafora, JW, 2007. Phylogenetic classification of Cordyceps and the clavicipitaceous fungi. Studies in Mycology 57: 5 - 69, DOI: https://doi.org/10.3114/sim.2007.57.01" title="Phylogenetic classification of Cordyceps and the clavicipitaceous fungi." url="https://doi.org/10.3114/sim.2007.57.01" volume="57" year="2007">Sung et al. (2007)</bibRefCitation>
revised it to 
<taxonomicName class="Ascomycetes" family="Ophiocordycipitaceae" genus="O." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="O. jiangxiensis" order="Hypocreales" pageId="0" pageNumber="79" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="jiangxiensis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="79">O. jiangxiensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
only based on the original morphological description. The species is closely similar to 
<taxonomicName class="Sordariomycetes" family="Clavicipitaceae" genus="Metarhizium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Metarhizium purpureonigrum" order="Hypocreales" pageId="0" pageNumber="79" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="purpureonigrum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="79">Metarhizium purpureonigrum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, a recently-described species from Thailand (
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.simyco.2020.04.001" author="Mongkolsamrit, S" journalOrPublisher="Studies in Mycology" pageId="0" pageNumber="79" pagination="171 - 251" refId="B61" refString="Mongkolsamrit, S, Khonsanit, A, Thanakitpipattana, D, Tasanathai, K, Noisripoom, W, Lamlertthon, S, Himaman, W, Houbraken, J, Samson, RA, Luangsa-ard, J, 2020. Revisiting Metarhizium and the description of new species from Thailand. Studies in Mycology 95: 171 - 251, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1016/j.simyco.2020.04.001" title="Revisiting Metarhizium and the description of new species from Thailand." url="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.simyco.2020.04.001" volume="95" year="2020">Mongkolsamrit et al. 2020</bibRefCitation>
). Future studies are warranted to clarify its taxonomic placement.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
